  <span id="freeText4650902027100687656" style="display:none">A possible present day dystopian novel involving a young girl, Mae, as the protagonist who starts in a dead end job, is divorced, has two parents, one of which is not well, and is also separated from her very best friend Annie. Annie works for the 'Circle', the number one internet management company in the world. <br />When Mae is hired at the 'Circle' with the help of her friend Annie, life-changing experiences lead her into a different world, a world we could all envision ourselves in someday.<br />My thoughts, the book was long for me, over 400 pages, drawn out, with a very unexpected ending. I'm not trying to say this in a negative fashion. I enjoyed the book. The story was made into a movie and I am looking forward to seeing it. 📙 🐦</span>
